# react-amnesia AI Docs Maintenance

This file is generated by `scripts/generate-agent-instructions.mjs`. Edit `website/docs/ai/*` and run `npm run docs:ai` instead of editing this file directly.

- Edit `website/docs/ai/*`, not the generated instruction packs.
- Re-run `npm run docs:ai` after changing the canonical AI docs.
- Re-run `npm run ai:check` before committing to catch drift.
